LoadCompletedEventHandler Delegate

Definition

Represents the method that will handle LoadCompleted events.

In this Article

public delegate void LoadCompletedEventHandler(object sender, NavigationEventArgs e);
Inheritance
Object
System.Delegate
LoadCompletedEventHandler

Remarks

This event handler is used for the following events:

  • System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.LoadCompleted
  • System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.LoadCompleted
  • System.Windows.Controls.Frame.LoadCompleted
  • System.Windows.Application.LoadCompleted
